Poetry - Project Setup

Manage dependencies in your Python project with [bold]poetry[/bold]. Use the [bold]add[/bold] subcommand to add new dependencies.

[dim]# Create a new project[/dim]
[bold green]$[/bold green] [bold]poetry new[/bold] [yellow]project-name[/yellow]            [dim]# Create new project at <project-name>[/dim]
[bold green]$[/bold green] [bold]poetry init[/bold]                        [dim]# Create a basic pyproject.toml in the current directory[/dim]

[dim]# Installing an existing project[/dim]
[bold green]$[/bold green] [bold]poetry install[/bold]                     [dim]# Install dependencies, and entrypoints, from pyproject.toml[/dim]
